🎯 Core Idea
A reminder system in a browser‑based AI workspace requires four components:

A data model to store reminders in IndexedDB

A scheduler that periodically checks for due reminders

A trigger mechanism(UI notification, chat message, or system alert)

AI integration so the bot can create, update, and explain reminders

This works even offline and stays isolated per workspace.

